        "title": "Mission: Possible - Designing Tomorrow's Learning Experience",
        "excerpt":" id: mission-possible title: ‚ÄúMission: Possible - Designing Tomorrow‚Äôs Learning Experience‚Äù speaker: robert-jensen excerpt: ‚ÄúCreating a learning platform can seem like a ‚ÄúMission: Impossible‚Äù. I have built and run several, with mixed results.‚Äù topics:      devops   platform-engineering   ai events:   2025-aarhus    Creating a learning platform can seem like a ‚ÄúMission: Impossible‚Äù. I have built and run several, with mixed results. This session is about my failures, my learnings, and my success in the end, with an open-source solution that can be implemented by any company with a need for providing training to their users. There will be live demos showcasing how to create both the platform, but also a DevOps training path.  ","categories": [],
