        "title": "Strategical PlatformOps with Wardley Maps",
        "excerpt":" id: platform-ops-wardley title: ‚ÄúStrategical PlatformOps with Wardley Maps‚Äù speaker: andrey-adamovich excerpt: ‚ÄúInternal platforms are crucial for empowering software teams, but their evolution presents strategic challenges. In this session, we‚Äôll embark on a journey using Wardley Maps to explore the platform engineering landscape together. Rather than offering definitive answers, we‚Äôll engage in a discussion to map out key elements, track their evolution, and uncover potential strategies. Through this collaborative process, we aim to spark new ideas and perspectives, enabling participants to better navigate the complexities of building and scaling internal platforms.‚Äù topics:      devops   platform-engineering   ai events:   2025-aarhus    Internal platforms are crucial for empowering software teams, but their evolution presents strategic challenges. In this session, we‚Äôll embark on a journey using Wardley Maps to explore the platform engineering landscape together. Rather than offering definitive answers, we‚Äôll engage in a discussion to map out key elements, track their evolution, and uncover potential strategies. Through this collaborative process, we aim to spark new ideas and perspectives, enabling participants to better navigate the complexities of building and scaling internal platforms.  ","categories": [],
