        "title": "Tackling complexity with a thin platform approach",
        "excerpt":"StudyHub is a suite of Digital Products centered around improving the planning of Clinical Trials within Novo Nordisk through the use of Agentic AI and an Event Driven backend.   This session will take a deep dive into how we have taken a thin platform approach across 7 digital products and used it to      increase reusability of infrastructure as code   increase use of pipeline templates   strive for simplicity   plug and play cloud infrastructure for software engineers, data engineers and data scientist   not compromise on flexibility and extendability   ease onboarding of new services   You will learn how we structure our infrastructure as code and pipelines with the consumer in mind, so they don‚Äôt have to create the same resources from scratch over and over again, avoid the hassle of configuring access, and instead focus on delivery value to our users  ","categories": [],
